## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="40a33-158">下面的代码示例将重置的几何变换的`pgBrush`到标识。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40a33-158">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40a33-159">假定`myPath`是现有<xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40a33-159">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
PathGradientBrush pgBrush = new PathGradientBrush(myPath);  
 pgBrush.ResetTransform();  
```
